headline: This Value Stock ETF Is Crushing the S&P 500. Here’s Its Secret Weapon.
summary: Value stocks are surging, thanks in part to tech stocks that have driven returns of the overall market.  Fortunately, there are still plenty of undervalued stocks for bargain hunters.  It hasn’t been a great era for value funds.
